room_title: Escape room "Jackpot!" by Mission Manor in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: "The House always wins," or so the saying goes. Well, you've got different plans for how this particular night is going to go. Your man on the inside has laid the breadcrumbs, all you have to do is follow them and you'll take the casino for all its worth, walking away wealthy beyond your wildest dreams. Ready to roll the dice?
